Achievements.Name: Season Mode Jobber
Achievements.Description: Complete Season Mode on easy or normal difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Season Mode Veteran
Achievements.Description: Complete Season Mode on hard difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Season Mode Legend
Achievements.Description: Complete Season Mode on legend difficulty.

Achievements.Name: New Hire
Achievements.Description: Complete one full year of General Manager Mode.

Achievements.Name: Employee of the year
Achievements.Description: Win the General Manager of the year trophy.

Achievements.Name: Royal Rumble Rookie
Achievements.Description: Win a 10 Man Exhibition Royal Rumble as the # 1 entrant on any difficulty setting.

Achievements.Name: Royal Rumble Jobber
Achievements.Description: Win a 15 Man Exhibition Royal Rumble as the # 1 entrant on any difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Royal Rumble Veteran
Achievements.Description: Win a 20 Man Exhibition Royal Rumble as the # 1 entrant on hard difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Royal Rumble Pro
Achievements.Description: Win a 25 Man Exhibition Royal Rumble as the #1 entrant on hard difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Royal Rumble Legend
Achievements.Description: Win a 30 Man Exhibition Royal Rumble as the #1 entrant on legend difficulty.

Achievements.Name: In Ring Journeyman
Achievements.Description: Win at least one match using every Superstar on the roster on any difficulty setting.

Achievements.Name: In Ring Technician
Achievements.Description: Defeat every Superstar on the roster by pin or submission at least once on hard difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Complete Domination!
Achievements.Description: Defeat every Superstar on the roster at least once on legend difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Championship Gold!
Achievements.Description: Unlock every WWE Championship title.

Achievements.Name: Those Who Paved The Way
Achievements.Description: Unlock every WWE Legend.

Achievements.Name: Way Past Jobber
Achievements.Description: Win 50 matches on any difficulty setting.

Achievements.Name: Seasoned Vet
Achievements.Description: Win 100 matches on any difficulty setting.

Achievements.Name: Online Rising Star
Achievements.Description: Win 20 matches online.

Achievements.Name: Online Veteran
Achievements.Description: Win 50 matches online.

Achievements.Name: Online Blue Chipper
Achievements.Description: Win 20 consecutive online matches.

Achievements.Name: Certified Online Superstar
Achievements.Description: Win 50 consecutive online matches.

Achievements.Name: A Fighting Online Champion
Achievements.Description: Defend your created Championship 20 times online.

Achievements.Name: Let It Reign!
Achievements.Description: Defend your created Championship 50 times online.

Achievements.Name: With Friends Like These...
Achievements.Description: Create an original stable of Superstars in Create-A-Stable mode.

Achievements.Name: Crown Us The Champ!
Achievements.Description: Create a Tag Team Championship in Create-A-Championship mode.

Achievements.Name: Self Anointed Champion
Achievements.Description: Create a singles Championship in Create-A-Championship mode.

Achievements.Name: Curtain Call
Achievements.Description: Create an original entrance in Create-An-Entrance mode.

Achievements.Name: Let The Creative Juices Flow
Achievements.Description: Create one original Superstar using the Create-A-Superstar mode.

Achievements.Name: Mr. PPV
Achievements.Description: Create an original PPV event in Create-A-PPV mode.
